{"tid":41735,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"無啦啦比人炒左","createTime":"2016-12-16T06:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T16:59:42.000Z","uid":43834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d60cb07c19a582f7209dda21d2524a00f2386448","tid":41735,"uid":43834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:08:03.000Z","msg":"今日公司發生左件事<br />\n話說我做批發既公司事<br />\n主要follow酒店order<br />\n有其他公司都要幫幫手接<br />\n話說琴日有個大order有人接左但無送貨<br />\n個客就好嬲就話唔會再幫襯我地<br />\n點知我個senior就屌9我話我錯<br />\n我死都話無 個manager見到我地嘈<br />\n就分別叫我入房<br />\n就話我唔適合呢份工<br />\n就立刻攞左份打左我名既信叫我簽名叫我走<br />\n我再嘈左勁耐話關我咩事<br />\n我話呢間公司我都係第一次聽呢個名<br />\n點會係我接<br />\n個manager話立刻走可以攞到7日待通知金<br />\n佢又話另外會有多7日糧補比你<br />\n心諗係咪身有屎 要幫住senior先揾我出氣<br />\n有少少後悔點解簽左名<br />\n依家無工番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 個senior係做左24年既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">死肥婆</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9baf4fffb5c27a6d35e7c4dd52370638eb766b","tid":41735,"uid":51512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:09:35.000Z","msg":"得罪肥婆預左架啦"},{"pid":"ca30a40dc587876ca8f1b0c6ca438eecdbf9d4df","tid":41735,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:19:58.000Z","msg":"無証無據點可以就咁就炒?<br />\n打番比個客 問佢當日係邊個接既<br />\n唔知咩名都問男定女 係咪我依把聲<br />\n之後囉上勞工處玩大佢"},{"pid":"2c65b3b5355f1e2031976a50d16a300db078c543","tid":41735,"uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:22:43.000Z","msg":"咁你做咩簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b54255a75124abfe140b4bce3c4085c00c7f10","tid":41735,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:29:57.000Z","msg":"上奴工處啦，先搵好證據證明唔係自己錯，佢就係不合理解僱"},{"pid":